trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject"></xref>s.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaObjectCollection" name="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" href=""></xref> class.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaObjectCollection" name="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" href=""></xref> class that takes an <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject"></xref>.
Adds an <xref href="System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaObject"></xref> to the <xref uid="langword_csharp_XmlSchemaObjectCollection" name="XmlSchemaObjectCollection" href=""></xref>.

If `Count` already equals the capacity, the capacity of list is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array and copying the existing elements to the new array before the new element is added.
If `Count` is less than the capacity, this method is an 0(1) operation.
If the capacity needs to be increased to accommodate the new element, this method becomes an 0(n) operation, where n is `Count`.

The Add method expects only <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaExternal> and its derived types (<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaImport>, <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaInclude>, and <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaRedefine>) as parameters.
The following example illustrates adding an included schema to the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema.Includes%2A> collection of an existing <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> object.

source.ph: ```vb# Dim schema As XmlSchema = New XmlSchema() Dim textReader As XmlTextReader = New XmlTextReader("include.xsd") Dim includeSchema As XmlSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null) Dim include As XmlSchemaInclude = New XmlSchemaInclude() include.Schema = includeSchema; schema.Includes.Add(include); ```

```c# XmlSchema schema = new XmlSchema(); XmlTextReader textReader = new XmlTextReader("include.xsd"); XmlSchema includeSchema = XmlSchema.Read(textReader, null); XmlSchemaInclude include = new XmlSchemaInclude(); include.Schema = includeSchema; schema.Includes.Add(include); ```
